  ### Who can get legal aid?

  * your income (or combined income if you have a partner) should not
    be more than £2,657 a month before tax
  * your savings (or combined savings if you have a partner) should not
    be more than £8,000
  * you (and your partner if you have one) should have no more than £733
    a month left after we've taken certain living expenses into account -
    this service will work this out for you
